01:36:14,640 --> 01:36:17,100
沒錯 你說什麼？
- That's correct. - Excuse me?

972
01:36:19,060 --> 01:36:21,310
我說沒錯
I said that is correct.

973
01:36:21,480 --> 01:36:25,940
你會替我們解釋這些 編碼賬目？
And you will decipher these coded entries for us?

974
01:36:28,740 --> 01:36:30,610
是的
I will.

975
01:36:30,780 --> 01:36:36,390
對不起，佩恩先生，我聽不到 是的，我會
Sorry, Mr Payne, I can't hear you. I said, I will.

976
01:36:36,540 --> 01:36:40,210
你負責替卡邦先生 開支費用？
You were in charge of disbursements for Mr Capone?

977
01:36:41,540 --> 01:36:42,750
是的
Yes, I was.

978
01:36:42,920 --> 01:36:45,960
你親自將那些
And you personally distributed monies...

979
01:36:46,130 --> 01:36:50,220
未報稅的巨款
..vast, undeclared monies...

980
01:36:50,380 --> 01:36:52,550
交給卡邦先生？
..to Mr Capone?

981
01:36:53,850 --> 01:36:55,220
是的
Yes, I did.

982
01:36:56,430 --> 01:36:58,390
你能告訴我總數嗎？
Would you tell us the amounts?

983
01:37:00,850 --> 01:37:02,940
三年來
In a three-year

984
01:37:03,100 --> 01:37:07,070
我親自交給卡邦先生
period I personally disbursed monies to Mr Capone

985
01:37:07,230 --> 01:37:12,070
一百三十多萬元
in excess of one and a third million dollars.

986
01:37:15,070 --> 01:37:18,580
請你再重複一次？
Would you repeat that amount, please?

987
01:37:18,750 --> 01:37:22,210
一百三十多萬元
- One and a third million dollars.

988
01:37:22,370 --> 01:37:24,710
非常感謝
- Thank you very much.

989
01:37:40,140 --> 01:37:43,140
我不明白 卡邦為何有持無恐？
I don't understand it. What does Capone have?

990
01:37:43,310 --> 01:37:45,770
我們把他逼到絕路 而他卻一直在微笑
We're nailing the lid on his coffin, and he's smiling.

991
01:38:10,670 --> 01:38:12,880
那狗娘養的在法庭上帶了槍
The son-of-a-bitch is wearing a gun in court.

992
01:38:16,970 --> 01:38:18,600
叫法警來
Get me the bailiff.

993
01:38:21,270 --> 01:38:23,270
很快會結束的
It'll be a fast trial.

994
01:38:26,270 --> 01:38:30,270
前排穿白西裝的人 身上帶了把槍
The man in the front row wearing a white suit is carrying a gun.

995
01:38:31,030 --> 01:38:34,150
我不想出什麼事 所以你抓他時
I don't want this to turn into something.

996
01:38:34,320 --> 01:38:36,490
我會帶你出去 是的，長官
I'll lead you out.

997
01:38:43,000 --> 01:38:44,870
能和你談會兒嗎？
Could we speak to you a minute, please?

998
01:39:14,030 --> 01:39:15,240
面對牆壁 你到底是誰？
- Get up against it.

999
01:39:16,360 --> 01:39:18,030
你聽到他的話了！ 面對牆壁！
- You heard him. Now, up against it!

1000
01:39:20,030 --> 01:39:21,240
這是幹嘛？
- What's this?

1001
01:39:21,410 --> 01:39:24,200
好了，把口袋掏空 放桌子上，全拿出來
- Empty all your pockets, all of it.

1002
01:39:24,370 --> 01:39:27,000
我有帶槍的許可 我看看
- I've got a permit for that. - Fine, let's see it.

1003
01:39:31,130 --> 01:39:32,880
遭起訴的人不是我
- I'm not the one under indictment.

1004
01:39:33,050 --> 01:39:34,550
把東西放在桌上
- Everything on the table.

1005
01:39:38,340 --> 01:39:40,510
給我看看 把槍還他
- Let me see. - Give him his gun back.

1006
01:39:40,680 --> 01:39:42,930
「相關人員看到此信 請通融一下」
"To Whom It May Concern. Please extend to the bearer,"

1007
01:39:43,100 --> 01:39:47,020
「請給予持有人法蘭克尼提先生 一切的方便」
"Mr Frank Nitti, all possible courtesy and consideration."

1008
01:39:47,190 --> 01:39:49,730
「威廉湯姆 芝加哥市長」
"William Thompson, Mayor of the City of Chicago."

1009
01:39:49,900 --> 01:39:51,860
對不起，奈斯先生 你必須把槍還給他
I'm sorry, Mr Ness, you'll have to give it back.

1010
01:39:53,400 --> 01:39:54,940
好吧
Fine.

1011
01:39:55,740 --> 01:39:59,240
但那傢伙不准再進入法庭 你明白嗎？
But that man does not go back into that courtroom. Do you understand me?

1012
01:39:59,240 --> 01:40:00,530
是的，長官
- Yes, sir.

1013
01:40:30,730 --> 01:40:33,060
（拉辛路1634號）
1634 Racine...

1014
01:40:34,270 --> 01:40:36,400
你知道嗎 我曾有位朋友住在那裏？
You know, I used to have a friend who lived there.

1015
01:40:50,370 --> 01:40:53,170
不要讓他走
Don't . Let him go.

1016
01:40:56,670 --> 01:40:59,800
不要！ 槍給你
- No! - Here, take it.

1017
01:45:10,380 --> 01:45:15,390
我在這兒呢，財政官員 來呀，逮捕我啊！
Here I am, Treasury Man. Come on! Harass me!

1018
01:45:17,180 --> 01:45:19,480
你在等什麼？
What are you waitin' for?

1019
01:45:20,270 --> 01:45:23,440
別光站在那裏！逮捕我呀！
Don't just stand there! Harass me!

1020
01:45:27,400 --> 01:45:29,490
別惹火我
Don't push me.

1021
01:45:32,530 --> 01:45:35,070
他們會燒死你的，老兄 是嗎？
- They're gonna burn you, buddy. - Yeah?

1022
01:45:35,240 --> 01:45:38,450
沒錯，我要看你被燒死 狗娘養的！
Yeah. I'm gonna come see you burn, you son-of-a-bitch!

1023
01:45:38,620 --> 01:45:41,000
因為你殺了我的朋友！
'Cause you killed my friend!

1024
01:45:41,160 --> 01:45:44,920
他死得像隻豬一樣 你說什麼？
- He died like a pig. - What did you say?

1025
01:45:45,080 --> 01:45:48,630
我說你朋友死前 哀號得像豬一樣
I said that your friend died screaming like a stuck Irish pig.

1026
01:45:48,800 --> 01:45:51,840
等我脫罪時，你慢慢想吧
Now you think about that when I beat the rap.

1027
01:46:05,940 --> 01:46:07,900
他聽起來是那樣嗎？
Did he sound anything like that?

1028
01:46:38,930 --> 01:46:41,430
拍張照，拍張照
One picture, come on, one picture.

1029
01:46:44,520 --> 01:46:46,520
奈斯先生，看看這個
Mr Ness, take a look at this.

1030
01:46:48,730 --> 01:46:50,020
奈斯先生？
Mr Ness?

1031
01:46:52,150 --> 01:46:55,650
奈斯先生，你還好嗎？ 你最好看看這個
Mr Ness, are you doin' okay? I think you'd better see this.

1032
01:46:57,820 --> 01:47:00,370
這是什麼？ 這是什麼？這是陪審團名單
- What is it? - That's the jury list, Mr Ness.

1033
01:47:00,530 --> 01:47:02,450
他們被收買了
They've been bribed.

1034
01:47:02,620 --> 01:47:04,330
從尼提的衣服裏搜出來的
I got it out of Nitti's coat.

1035
01:47:05,210 --> 01:47:06,580
尼提呢？
Where is Nitti?

1036
01:47:08,460 --> 01:47:10,460
他在車上
He's in the car.

1037
01:47:29,360 --> 01:47:32,610
這構不成證據 沒有出處
This constitutes no evidence

1038
01:47:32,780 --> 01:47:35,190
我可不允許… 庭上，事實是
. I'm not about to allow...Your Honour, the truth is

1039
01:47:35,360 --> 01:47:38,280
卡邦是個殺人兇手 並且將他無罪釋放
that Capone is a killer and he will go free.

1040
01:47:39,530 --> 01:47:42,950
對付他這種人只有一種辦法 那就是追捕他直至抓獲
There is only one way to deal with such men, and that is hunt them down.

1041
01:47:44,790 --> 01:47:46,790
這樣做了我違背了我的誓言
I have. I have forsworn myself.

1042
01:47:46,960 --> 01:47:48,790
我違背了我誓言 要維護的一切法律
I have broken laws I swore to defend.

1043
01:47:48,960 --> 01:47:51,500
我成了我想成的人 我很滿意我做的事
I am content that I have done right.

1044
01:47:51,670 --> 01:47:53,380
必須阻止那個人你必須…
That man must be stopped, you must...

1045
01:47:53,550 --> 01:47:57,050
我將判斷我必須做的事 奈斯先生
I'll be the judge of what I must do, Mr Ness.

1046
01:48:07,270 --> 01:48:09,310
請允許我們離開
Would you excuse us?

1047
01:49:12,000 --> 01:49:13,830
法警 是，長官
- Bailiff. - Yes, sir.

1048
01:49:18,630 --> 01:49:21,220
法警 我要你去隔壁霍夫曼的法庭
I want you to go next door to Judge Hoffman's Court,

1049
01:49:21,380 --> 01:49:24,300
他們剛開始聽證離婚案
where they've just begun hearing a divorce action.

1050
01:49:24,470 --> 01:49:30,100
我要你把那兒陪審團帶來 把這裏的陪審團帶過去
I want you to bring that jury in here and take this jury to his court.

1051
01:49:31,850 --> 01:49:35,560
法警，你聽清楚了嗎 是的，長官，我明白
- Are those instructions clear? - Yes, sir, they're clear.

1052
01:49:36,520 --> 01:49:38,230
他說什麼？這在幹嘛？
What's he talking about?

1053
01:49:39,990 --> 01:49:43,360
我要你調換陪審團
Bailiff, I want you to switch the juries.

1054
01:49:44,070 --> 01:49:45,870
是的，長官 庭上，我反對！
Your Honour, I object!

1055
01:49:47,160 --> 01:49:48,660
駁回
Overruled.

1056
01:49:53,330 --> 01:49:55,040
你跟他說什麼了？
What did you tell him?

1057
01:49:56,840 --> 01:49:59,460
我說他的名字也在帳簿上
I told him his name was in the ledger, too.

1058
01:50:01,470 --> 01:50:03,090
但他的名字並不在帳簿上
His name wasn't in the ledger!

1059
01:50:04,720 --> 01:50:07,390
等等這就是法律？ 那兒怎麼了？
Wait a second! Is this the law? What's goin' on here?

1060
01:50:07,550 --> 01:50:09,220
你不守規矩 那兒怎麼了？
- You're out of order. - What's goin' on?

1061
01:50:09,390 --> 01:50:12,640
我認為我們必須… 我不在乎做點什麼
- I think... - Do somethin' here.

1062
01:50:12,810 --> 01:50:15,480
你怎麼看我？ 做點什麼做點什麼！
What do I look like to you? Do somethin'

1063
01:50:16,100 --> 01:50:17,560
肅靜！
Order!

1064
01:50:19,270 --> 01:50:22,530
庭上，我們撤回無罪申辯…
Your Honour, we'd like to withdraw our plea of Not Guilty,

1065
01:50:23,530 --> 01:50:25,610
…改為有罪申辯
and enter a plea of Guilty.

1066
01:50:29,490 --> 01:50:31,910
有罪？ 法庭上肅靜！
- Guilty? - Order in the court!

1067
01:50:32,080 --> 01:50:33,330
肅靜！
Order!

1068
01:50:34,410 --> 01:50:36,210
有罪！
Guilty

1069
01:50:42,800 --> 01:50:46,220
法警！我說，肅靜！ 庭上！
Bailiff! Bailiff!

1070
01:50:46,390 --> 01:50:49,140
法警，肅清法庭！ 庭上！
Bailiff, clear the courtroom!

1071
01:50:49,300 --> 01:50:51,470
我這兒需要控制一下！ 艾略特奈斯
Eliot!

1072
01:50:51,640 --> 01:50:54,850
庭上！ 庭上，這公正嗎？
Your Honour! Is that justice?

1073
01:50:55,020 --> 01:50:57,770
他為什麼要調換陪審團？
Please, why did he switch the jury?

1074
01:50:57,940 --> 01:51:00,570
你現在要幹嘛？ 繼續跟著組織？
Are you gonna go after the organisation?

1075
01:51:00,730 --> 01:51:02,320
抱歉
Excuse me.

1076
01:51:03,570 --> 01:51:06,450
請問庭上，這公正嗎？
I'm askin' Your Honour, is this justice?

1077
01:51:07,610 --> 01:51:09,160
正義何在？
What justice ?

1078
01:51:10,740 --> 01:51:13,250
庭上！這樣公正嗎？
Is this justice?

1079
01:51:13,250 --> 01:51:14,910
等等，等等，等等！
Wait,Wait,Wait,Wait,

1080
01:51:15,580 --> 01:51:16,670
等等！
Wait,

1081
01:51:17,120 --> 01:51:19,960
絕不停止，絕不停止戰鬥 直到戰鬥終止
Never stop fighting till the fight is done.

1082
01:51:20,130 --> 01:51:21,630
他說什麼？你在說什麼？
What did you say?

1083
01:51:21,800 --> 01:51:24,970
我說絕不停止戰鬥 直到戰鬥終止
I said, never stop fighting till the fight is done.

1084
01:51:25,130 --> 01:51:27,930
什麼？ 你聽到了，卡邦，都結束了
- What? - You heard me, Capone. It's over.

1085
01:51:28,090 --> 01:51:29,970
滾開，你只會說大話
You're nothin' but a lot of talk and a badge.

1086
01:51:30,140 --> 01:51:33,350
最後一課 你只知道口出狂言
Here endeth the lesson.

1087
01:51:33,520 --> 01:51:35,520
你只知道口出狂言！
You're nothin' but a lot of talk and a badge!

1088
01:51:35,680 --> 01:51:37,730
你只知道口出狂言！
You're nothin' but a lot of talk and a badge!

1089
01:51:37,900 --> 01:51:40,110
你只知道口出狂言！
You're nothin' but a lot of talk and a badge!

1090
01:51:56,580 --> 01:52:01,250
「鐵面無私 打擊罪犯」

1091
01:52:01,420 --> 01:52:04,130
「奈斯保證不被收買」

1092
01:52:05,130 --> 01:52:07,630
「卡邦今天出庭」

1093
01:52:08,880 --> 01:52:12,930
「卡邦被判十一年徒刑 今天開始執行」

1094
01:52:58,890 --> 01:53:01,020
太多暴力了
So much violence.

1095
01:54:07,210 --> 01:54:08,920
總算清理了一點
Cleaning up a little.

1096
01:54:19,220 --> 01:54:21,310
我想該說再見了
I guess this is goodbye.

1097
01:54:23,060 --> 01:54:24,440
再見，喬治史東
Goodbye, George.

1098
01:54:26,980 --> 01:54:30,150
我要…為此感謝你
I want to...thank you for this.

1099
01:54:31,030 --> 01:54:33,030
不，謝謝你
No. Thank you.

1100
01:54:48,790 --> 01:54:52,590
奈斯先生，我認為他希望 你能保有它
Mr Ness... I think he would have wanted you to have that.

1101
01:54:53,760 --> 01:54:55,340
不，他希望送給警員
He'd have wanted a cop to have it.

1102
01:55:00,350 --> 01:55:01,680
我要回家了
I'm going home.

1103
01:55:13,900 --> 01:55:16,700
奈斯先生！ 你對這標題有何意見？
Mr Ness! Any comment for the record?

1104
01:55:16,860 --> 01:55:19,490
「當場捉拿卡邦的人」
'The man who put Al Capone on the spot.'

1105
01:55:19,660 --> 01:55:22,200
我只是適逢其時而已
I just happened to be there when the wheel went round.

1106
01:55:22,370 --> 01:55:24,540
聽說禁酒令將取消
They say they're going to repeal prohibition.

1107
01:55:25,370 --> 01:55:26,830
你會怎麼做？
- What will you do then?

1108
01:55:28,460 --> 01:55:30,170
也許我會去喝上一杯
- I think I'll have a drink.


